ðŸ” What it does:

    For each student:

        If marks â‰¥ 90 â†’ show â€œExcellentâ€

        Else if â‰¥ 75 â†’ â€œGoodâ€

        Else if â‰¥ 50 â†’ â€œAverageâ€

        Else â†’ â€œPoorâ€

